title: MANUAL OF THE PLANES DND 4E
description:
Beyond the mortal world awaits great peril, power, and  adventure. Welcome to the planes! With this book, you can 
explore the magical realms of the Feywild, the haunted lands of the Shadowfell, the divine dominions of the Astral Sea, and the savage maelstrom of the Elemental Chaos and the Abyss. Every plane offers unique adventuring locations filled with unparalleled dangers and fantastic features. 

This supplement for the Dungeons & DragonsÃƒâ€šÃ‚Â® Roleplaying Game explores the planes of existence, including the Feywild, the Shadowfell, the Astral Sea, and the Elemental Chaos. In addition to planar monsters and hazards for Dungeon Masters, this book features new paragon paths, feats, rituals, and magic items for players looking for an edge when adventuring in the planes.
